    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "いち、に、さん、し、ごー、ろく、しち、はち……\nふー、準備運動も出来たしそろそろ走りに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "One‚ two‚ three‚ four‚ five‚ six‚ seven‚ eight…\nPhew‚ warm-up's done. Time for a run…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふふーん～ふんふふ～んポテトチップス～\nふふーふんふんポテポテポテトチップス～ふんふん～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hum-hu-hum~ Hum-hu-hum~ Potato chips~\nHe-he~ Hum-hum‚ poty-poty potato chips~ Hum-hum~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 133.33333340000132
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "あら、すず？\n随分ご機嫌そうだけど……どこ行くの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ Suzu?\nYou're in a great mood… Where are you going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃあっ！？　れれれれれ怜！？\nべべべべちゅにどこにも行きまえんわよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hieeek!? R-r-r-r-r-Rei!?\nI-I-I-I'm not going anywhere in particular!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "何よ、その慌てっぷりは……もしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's with all the panicking… Don't tell me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "子ども扱いしないでくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stop treating me like a child!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まだ何も言ってないけど……まあいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven't even said anything yet… Well‚ whatever",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ何をするつもりだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then what were you planning to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2661040623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えーと、そのー、えー。あっ、そうですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you see‚ um… Oh‚ that's it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "私も怜と同じで食後の散歩にでも行こうかと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking of going for a post-dinner walk‚ just like you‚ Rei!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "へー、それなら公園の方まで一緒に走りに行かない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? In that case‚ why don't we go for a run together toward the park?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遠慮しておきますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll have to decline",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "私はあっちに散歩に行くので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I'm going for a walk that way",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "あっちってスーパーの方よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"That way\" is toward the supermarket",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうでしたかしら？　ま、まあ……\n別にスーパーに用事などありませんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-was it? Well‚ I mean…\nIt's not like I have any business at the supermarket",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "そうよね。まさかこんな時間にこっそりポテトチップス\nを買いに行ったりなんてしないわよね？　まさかね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure you don't. You wouldn't be sneaking out at this hour\nto buy potato chips‚ would you? Surely not?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まさかまさかですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surely not‚ of course!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなまさかあるはずありませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way that could ever be the case!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ一緒に走りに行きましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then let's go for a run together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "早くトレーニングウェアに着替えてきて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Go change into your workout gear‚ quickly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……分かりましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Understood",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "今日のところは、諦めるしかありませんわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I have no choice but to give up for today",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few minutes later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6493425052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "お待たせしました。走りに行きますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to keep you waiting. Let's go for our run",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええ。ところで……なんでポテトチップスのカスが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure. By the way… Why are there potato chip crumbs",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8333272298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.8333272298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_04-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "口の周りに付いているのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "stuck around your mouth?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どどどどどこに付いてるんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-w-w-w-where are they!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyohall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyohall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.2666605632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
